## 🌍 Real-World Application

Many organizations host multiple internal applications on a single Apache or Nginx server.

Examples include:

- Internal Documentation Portal
- HR Portal
- Monitoring Dashboard
- Company Wiki
- Status Page

Rather than provisioning a server for every application, multiple sites can be served efficiently using URL paths or virtual hosts.

